NAME

    Device::LPS331AP - I2C interface to LPS331AP Thermometer and Barometer
    using Device::SMBus

VERSION

    version 0.006

ATTRIBUTES

 I2CBusDevicePath

    this is the device file path for your I2CBus that the LPS331AP is
    connected on e.g. /dev/i2c-1 This must be provided during object
    creation.

 Altimeter

        $self->Altimeter->enable();
        $self->Altimeter->getReading();

    This is a object of Device::Altimeter::LPS331AP

